Variables:
- claim: object, contains information about the claim
- responseMessage: string, stores the user's response message
- formSubmitted: boolean, tracks whether the form has been submitted

Constants:
- mat-h2: string, styling class for the h2 element
- mat-subheading-2: string, styling class for the subheading element
- mat-body-1: string, styling class for the body text elements
- yyyy/MM/dd: string, date format for the claim date
- mat-label: string, label for the input field
- mat-raised-button: string, styling class for the raised button element
- primary: string, color for the primary button
- warn: string, color for the warning button

ViewChild:
- None

Functions:
- onSubmit(): void, function to handle form submission
- onCancel(): void, function to handle cancellation of form submission